## 3. Action Plan (Job-Ready Polish)

### Phase 1: Standardization (High Priority)
1.  **Audit & Replace Colors**:
    -   Scan all `*.jsx` files for `#` hex codes.
    -   Replace instances with their semantic equivalent (e.g., `text-[#2D5A41]` â†’ `text-brand-primary`).
    -   Verify the `dark` mode appearance after changes.

2.  **Centralize Typography**:
    -   Avoid arbitrary pixel values like `text-[94px]`.
    -   Define a standard display size in Tailwind config or [index.css](file:///home/rocky/Projects/Pet-Adoption-Platform-Django-React/frontend/src/index.css) (e.g., `.text-display-lg`).

### Phase 2: Refactoring (Medium Priority)
3.  **Extract Navigation Components**:
    -   Create `src/components/common/Navigation/NavLink.jsx`.
    -   Move the hover/active logic from [Navbar](file:///home/rocky/Projects/Pet-Adoption-Platform-Django-React/frontend/src/components/common/Navbar.jsx#15-248) into this component.

4.  **Unify Animations**:
    -   Move the `marquee` keyframes from [HeroSection](file:///home/rocky/Projects/Pet-Adoption-Platform-Django-React/frontend/src/components/LandingPage/HeroSection.jsx#14-235) to [index.css](file:///home/rocky/Projects/Pet-Adoption-Platform-Django-React/frontend/src/index.css) as a utility class `.animate-marquee`.
    -   Remove the `<style jsx>` block.

### Phase 3: Layout Hardening (Low Priority)
5.  **Fix Hero Layout**:
    -   Use Flexbox `flex-1` instead of `calc(100vh - ...)` to fill available space naturally.
    -   Remove negative margins (`-mt-10`) in favor of proper spacing or `items-center`.

